- pycharm install
	- http://ubuntuhandbook.org/index.php/2016/07/latest-pycharm-ubuntu-16-04-ppa/
	- or
		- download pycharm from websit
		- https://www.jetbrains.com/pycharm-edu/quickstart/installation.html#linux
	- install git
		- sudo apt-get install git-core
	- create launcher
		- see doc typs linux
	- start pycharm: /home/bodgi/download/pycharm....../bin/pycharm.sh
	- git config
	    - git config --global user.email "gillesbodson@live.be"
        - https://help.github.com/articles/setting-your-email-in-git/

    - if pycharm doesn't seem to remember github password, look at: https://www.jetbrains.com/help/pycharm/2016.3/passwords.html


